Joseph O'Riordan was sitting on Polegate Town Council in East Sussex . 
  He grew suspicious his wife Amanda was having an affair . 
  He hired a private investigator to follow her and discovered she was in a relationship with their postman Nicholas Gunn . 
  He stabbed his wife eight times with a seven inch kitchen knife . 
  She was stabbed in the chest, torso, arms and back . 
  He pleaded guilty to wounding with intent but denied attempted murder . 
 